## 2026-04 Compact Top Area Update

To increase usable content above the fold, reduce vertical density of intro and section headers.

### A) Hero / Intro Card (All pages)
- Decrease hero padding (desktop and mobile).
- Reduce title size clearly from previous display scale.
- Reduce description size by one level.
- Tighten title-description gap and hero bottom margin.
- Keep the same soft gradient tone, but prioritize actionable controls.

### B) Section Title and Card Density
- Section titles should be smaller than before.
- Reduce card internal vertical padding and gaps.
- Keep readability, but avoid large blank areas.
- Ensure key controls (root/type selection and results) appear earlier on laptop screens.

### C) Responsive Direction
- Apply the same compact strategy to tablet and mobile.
- Mobile title/description should be further reduced slightly.
- Do not sacrifice tap target usability for tabs/buttons.

### D) Friendly Menu Descriptions (Short, Easy)
- 코드찾기: `루트와 코드 타입을 고르면 운지를 바로 확인할 수 있어요.`
- 코드수정: `코드 모양을 직접 바꾸고 저장할 수 있어요.`
- 조변환: `원래 코드를 원하는 키로 쉽게 바꿔볼 수 있어요.`

### E) Finder Section Labels
- Use concise labels:
  - `루트음`
  - `코드 타입`
  - `운지방법`

