## 2026-04 Shared layout density (three menus)

Applied consistently to **코드찾기**, **코드수정**, **조변환** via shared classes in `App.css` (`chord-finder__hero`, `section-card`, `chord-finder__heading`, `chord-finder__workspace`, etc.).

### Principles (must follow)

1. **소개 영역보다 실제 조작 UI를 우선 배치** — Intro/hero stays short; selection and results move up.
2. **상단 카드/타이틀/설명/섹션 제목은 과하게 크지 않게 유지** — Hero title ~18px desktop / ~16px compact; description ~12px; section headings ~14px.
3. **카드 상하 패딩과 섹션 간격은 전체 화면 밀도를 해치지 않는 수준으로 조정** — `section-card` padding ~8–10px; workspace gap ~8px; panel column gaps tightened.
4. **세 메뉴 전체에 공통으로 적용되는 기본 레이아웃 밀도를 일관되게 유지** — Same tokens for all three routes; per-menu layout tweaks are a separate step.

### Responsive (common)

- Page flow stays **vertical stack** on mobile/tablet/desktop.
- **No horizontal page scroll**: `.app-shell { overflow-x: hidden }`, main column `min-width: 0`; wide tables may scroll inside their own wrapper only.
- **Chord finder** has dedicated mobile flow (see **Chord finder screen — mobile flow**); other menus may follow separately.

### Implementation snapshot (reference)

| Element | Approx. desktop / compact |
|--------|---------------------------|
| Hero padding | ~8px 12px / compact ~7px 11px |
| Hero title | ~18px / compact ~16px |
| Hero description | ~12px (caption-ish) |
| Title–description gap | ~3px |
| Section heading (`.chord-finder__heading`) | ~14px |
| Section card padding | ~8–10px; internal gap ~6px |
| Workspace grid gap (wide) | ~12px |

### Radius scale (2026-04, tool-like)

Cards are **less round** than before; chips/tabs stay **fully rounded** for affordance.

| Token | Value | Typical use |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| `--radius-lg` | **12px** | Hero / top intro card (`.chord-finder__hero`) |
| `--radius-md` | **10px** | Section cards, result cards, selected summary, banners |
| `--radius-sm` | **8px** | Inputs, compact actions, nested items |
| `--radius-pill` | **999px** | Tab chips, pill toggles (rounder than cards) |

### Chord finder screen — structure & mobile (2026-04)

**Vertical order (DOM, top → bottom)** — must stay stable; **hero / title is always first**; nothing (e.g. fallback messages) may appear above the title.

1. **Title + description** (`.chord-finder__hero`)
2. **Chord finding** (`.chord-finder__workspace`): loading hint *or* main body
3. **Tail** (`.chord-finder__tail`): optional API/fallback notice, then **로그인** link (last)

**Mobile cognitive flow (루트음 | 코드 타입 | 운지)**

- **No page-level horizontal scroll.**
- Use a **3-column CSS grid** roughly **30% | 30% | 40%** (`0.3fr 0.3fr 0.4fr`): column 1 = 루트음 (vertical scroll list of tabs), column 2 = 코드 타입 (vertical tabs), column 3 = **선택 코드 이름만** (no “현재 코드” label) + **운지방법** (diagrams). Vertical tab lists use a **taller** `max-height` (e.g. ~`min(65vh, 520px)`) so more options show before scroll on typical phones.
- Implement with `display: contents` on `.chord-finder__pick-shell` so two rails + out column are **three grid items** on small screens.
- **`getChordReadingLabel`**: spaced label (e.g. `C sus4`).

**Tablet / desktop (≥768px)**

- **Two columns**: left = one card (`.chord-finder__pick-shell`) with 루트음 stacked above 코드 타입 (divider); horizontal tab strips restored via CSS on `.tab-strip--vertical` inside the shell.
- Right column: **선택 코드 텍스트** + 운지방법 card, left-aligned; chord name only (no extra label).

**Copy (fixed)**

- Title: `우쿨렐레 코드 찾기`
- Description: `루트와 코드 타입을 고르면 운지를 바로 확인할 수 있어요.`
- Labels: `루트음`, `코드 타입`, `운지방법` (never “Shape 목록”).

### Chord edit screen — structure & flow (2026-04)

**Goal:** Same **product tone** as chord finder (hero, card radius, tab density, 3-column mobile picker) while optimizing the **select → confirm → edit → apply** admin flow.

**Vertical order (DOM, top → bottom)**

1. **Title + description** (`.chord-finder__hero.chord-finder__hero--compact`): title `코드 수정`, description `코드 모양을 직접 바꾸고 저장할 수 있어요.` — short, not taller than finder hero.
2. **Workspace** (`.chord-finder__workspace.chord-edit__workspace`): same **`.chord-finder__body`** grid as finder — **루트음 (표준)** | **코드 타입** | **수정 열** (current chord name + 운지방법 card).
3. **Footer** (`.chord-edit__admin-foot`): 로그아웃 / 로그인 link — compact margin.

**Mobile**

- **No page-level horizontal scroll** (`.chord-edit { overflow-x: hidden; min-width: 0 }`).
- **3-column** picker matches finder (~30% / ~30% / ~40%); vertical tab strips with same `max-height` behavior as finder.
- **Current chord** in third column: **name only** (use `getChordReadingLabel`, same style as finder `.chord-finder__current`), `aria-label` like “수정 중인 코드 …”.
- **운지방법** card: status lines (loading / errors / empty) in a **compact** block (`.chord-edit__status`), then list rows labeled **운지방법 1…n** (never “Shape”). Primary action **`적용 / 저장`**; secondary **`운지방법 추가`**.

**Tablet / desktop (≥768px)**

- Same **two-column** split as finder: left shell = 루트 + 타입 (tabs become horizontal wrap); right = current name + 운지방법 editor.

**Copy (fixed)**

- Title: `코드 수정`
- Description: `코드 모양을 직접 바꾸고 저장할 수 있어요.`
- Never use “Shape 목록” / “shape 추가”; use **운지방법** wording throughout.

