## 5-8. Chord Result Card

### Purpose

Display one chord fingering result.

### Content

* Chord title
* Chord diagram
* Optional metadata or action buttons

### Style

* Padding: **14px** (or compact **~10px** when aligned with `.chord-card` in app)
* Border radius: **10px** (`--radius-md`), same family as section cards
* Border: `1px solid #E5ECF3`
* Internal gap: **10px**
* Background: `#FFFFFF`

### Chord Name

* Use **Chord Title**
* 18px / 700 / 1.2

### Description / Meta

* 14px / 400 / 1.55

### Layout Rule

* Desktop: support up to 4 result cards without excessive vertical growth
* Use 4-column or 2x2 layout depending on available width
* Do not make cards unnecessarily tall

### Mobile

* Prefer 1-column if diagram readability becomes too small
* 2-column is acceptable only if diagram still reads clearly

